{"tid":1647467,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[不分化] [免中伏] 出Post有責任, 回Post請留意, 我們能改善","createTime":"2019-10-11T18:15:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T04:39:13.000Z","uid":320881,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"047a7a1adf6208badf9c57e5c014b65cc19eb850","tid":1647467,"uid":320881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T18:15:31.000Z","msg":"先利申: P牌一名, 如不完美, 但可接受, 請輕力插, 會改善的<br />\n<br />\n眼見呢個<span style=\"color: red;\">無FC又有大量疑似五毛嘅post</span>, 同埋呢排出現一堆話要打埋左膠/消防一份嘅post, 仲要<span style=\"color: red;\">上埋熱門</span>, 本P牌表示很傷心<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1647267/page/2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1647267/page/2</a><br />\n補充: 雖然樓主係炒左車, 不過見佢有係內容打未FC, 後面又肯認錯, 比返隻連豬你啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以有以下建議/提醒<br />\n<br />\n<ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">出Post者</span></span></ins><br />\n如非單純轉載其他人意見之類, 而係講緊一件事, 就算你<span style=\"color: red;\">標題</span>唔<span style=\"color: red;\">寫[未FC] / [已FC]</span>, 麻煩係內容都<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大大隻字寫住未FC / 已FC</span></span>, 免得有班傻仔睇完張圖就信左<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">回Post者</span></span></ins><br />\n留意下樓主有無FC, 無FC<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好輕易下定論好無</span>? <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">特別係左膠post/消防post</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n起一<span style=\"color: red;\">起底</span>會發現入面有大量reply <span style=\"color: red;\">(特別係頭果堆)</span> 係<span style=\"color: red;\">空AC</span>/平時唔會係時事台開POST<br />\n所以麻煩要時刻保持獨立思考, 唔好好似D藍絲咁, 聽乜信乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n亦都提一提2個基本功<br />\n1. 唔係一張圖/fb/whatsapp之類就叫FC左, 要製造出黎有幾難?<br />\n2. 當發現係Fake news, 麻煩<span style=\"color: red;\">善用不推文回覆拉返佢落去</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後想補返句<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不篤灰, 不分化, 不割席</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"fde0a3c40cb471f439b7fdf12fc6446dac9d4514","tid":1647467,"uid":231583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T18:27:19.000Z","msg":"咁夜出post好少人睇<br />\n幫你推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54645a2736461cb11b103096224e952594e95cee","tid":1647467,"uid":320881,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fde0a3c40cb471f439b7fdf12fc6446dac9d4514","tid":1647467,"uid":231583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T18:27:19.000Z","msg":"咁夜出post好少人睇<br />\n幫你推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T18:30:17.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打, 我P牌想自己推都唔得<br />\n1日出得1篇, 如果聽朝先出post, 又怕星期日要出果陣出唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f87899cf894df39c294e90ca63806d683e26af1","tid":1647467,"uid":231583,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"54645a2736461cb11b103096224e952594e95cee","tid":1647467,"uid":320881,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fde0a3c40cb471f439b7fdf12fc6446dac9d4514","tid":1647467,"uid":231583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T18:27:19.000Z","msg":"咁夜出post好少人睇<br />\n幫你推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T18:30:17.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打, 我P牌想自己推都唔得<br />\n1日出得1篇, 如果聽朝先出post, 又怕星期日要出果陣出唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T18:33:28.000Z","msg":"其實時事台太大流量啦，自推都無咩用，而家推幾次就會失效<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" 